### Product Management API Testing
### Base URL: http://localhost:3000/api/admin/products
### Requires: Admin authentication token

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/admin
@token = YOUR_ADMIN_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Get All Products (with pagination)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?page=1&limit=10
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 2. Get All Products (with search)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?search=BM50
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 3. Get All Products (with filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/products?product_type=bm_account&stock_status=available
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 4. Get Product by ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 5. Get Product Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/products/stats
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 6. Create New Product
POST {{baseUrl}}/products
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_name": "BM100 - Premium",
  "product_type": "bm_account",
  "category": "bm100",
  "description": "Business Manager account with $100 spending limit",
  "price": 200000,
  "stock_status": "available",
  "is_active": true
}

### 7. Update Product
PUT {{baseUrl}}/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "product_name": "BM100 - Premium (Updated)",
  "price": 220000,
  "stock_status": "available"
}

### 8. Duplicate Product (NEW!)
POST {{baseUrl}}/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE/duplicate
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### 9. Delete Product
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/products/PRODUCT_ID_HERE
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

